window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>How did I get here? My assistant, bent on one knee, holding my hand, her expectant face waiting for an answer.... Just...how? </b></p> <p>How did I go from being insulted by Charlee Cox to hiring her to be my assistant? How is it that she’s chaos in color - making me crazy and my life better at the same time? </p> <p>I never thought I would be staring down at her bright blue eyes begging me to go along with the ridiculous scheme I suggested. </p> <p>Yes, I suggested it. Like the idiot I am, I thought hey, why not start an HR nightmare and have my assistant ask me to marry her? </p> <p>Confused? Don’t worry, so am I. </p> <p>But try to follow along, because this is how I became <i>Boss Man Bridegroom</i>.</p>"; 
